  物化探方法在圈定半隐伏超基性岩体中的应用—以青海省都兰县希望沟地区为例
  Search for Semi-Concealed Ultrabasic Rock Bodies Using Geophysical and Geochemical Methods—An Example from the Xiwanggou Area of Doulan, Qinghai
 
